The original version of this app is written Philipp Kern and doesn't work on newer Android versions. It can be downloaded here: https://code.google.com/p/kitcard-reader/

Kudos go to Fabian Knittel for his persistence in getting the reverse
engineering done.

For the app development thanks go to Isabel Slawik and Daniel Lemcke
who gave valuable tips for the design of the app.

Michael Gehle provided further input on the card's data.
